        <item>
            <title>Apple Watch 被指有「誤觸」情況，外媒：Apple 內部文件承認問題</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/13/apple-watch-touch-issue/mobile-phone/phone-parts/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-watch-touch-issue</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/13/apple-watch-touch-issue/mobile-phone/phone-parts/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 10:00:20 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手機配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[潮流手錶]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[apple watch]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1229059</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>早前有 Apple Watch 用户發現，手錶出現無故誤觸情況。在沒有觸碰手錶熒幕的情況下，手機畫面被不規則的自動按動，有用户的手錶更被自動輸入密碼，被回報「密碼錯誤，請 3 小時後再試」。有消息指 Apple 向授權維修供應商提醒不要為出現此狀況的用户更換手錶，而是建議用户等待下一次軟件更新。</p><p>根據報道，早在 2 月時 Apple 已向授權維修供應商提到 Apple Watch 誤觸情況，問題影響 Apple Watch Series 9、Apple Watch Ultra 2。其後有報告指災情擴展到 Apple Watch Series 7, 8，以及第一代 Apple Watch Ultra。報道指，Apple 提醒授權維修商不要因此問題而為用户更換手錶，只需向用户提示按住 Apple Watch 上兩個按鈕 10 秒鐘來強制重新啟動手錶便可，並確保手錶維持在最新的 watchOS。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">This has JUST been extended to series 7, series 8, as well as ultra 1 just FYI</p><p>Apple has advised us not to replace watches for this issue and to tell people to basically force restart the watch by holding both buttons together for 10 seconds and also keep your watches up-to-date <a href="https://t.co/klrVeYhkD0">https://t.co/klrVeYhkD0</a></p><p>&mdash; Stella &#8211; Fudge (@StellaFudge) <a href="https://twitter.com/StellaFudge/status/1778197004029394994?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">April 10, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>早前有用户指 Apple Watch 無故被觸動的情況，令他們難於使用手錶，有些人需要重新開機。而用户如遇到這種情況，可留意最新版 watchOS 更新。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_33708"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/m9OJDSIyu3M?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://technews.tw/2024/04/12/apple-watch-ghosttouches/">TechNews.tw</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/01/apples-website-finally-has-tech-specs-pages-for-apple-watch-models/parts/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Watch 官網終於展示技術規格　之前未有個別展示詳細規格</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/25/apple-watch-consider-support-android/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple 回應美國司法部壟斷指控，曾研究 Apple Watch 支援 Android 手機</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/05/hermes-apple-watch/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">全新 Hermès Apple Watch 錶帶登場，與其他系列共新增 22 款</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/13/apple-watch-touch-issue/mobile-phone/phone-parts/">Apple Watch 被指有「誤觸」情況，外媒：Apple 內部文件承認問題</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
