        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Mercedes-Maybach EQS 680 SUV 電車到港，雙色系型格車身、超豪內籠搶先睇</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/13/mercedes-maybach-eqs-680-suv/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mercedes-maybach-eqs-680-suv</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/13/mercedes-maybach-eqs-680-suv/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 07:00:25 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mercedes-Maybach]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mercedes-Maybach EQS 680 SUV]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1229022</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Maybach 品牌的首款全電動車款 Mercedes-Maybach EQS 680 SUV 近日正式到港。日前就在商場舉辦活動，就等小編一齊同大家去睇睇新車各種設計。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229025" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_123213-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_123213-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_123213.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229026" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_123240-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_123240-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_123240.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Mercedes-Maybach EQS 680 SUV 車頭設有經典的黑色面板和垂直的鍍鉻裝飾條，突顯出立體外觀輪廓。引擎蓋上鑲嵌著平治星型標誌，黑色的大型面板則首次以閉合方式設計。車身側面突顯了鍍鉻邊框和鍍鉻的 B 柱裝飾，後排座椅區域長度由此突出。車尾則裝飾有連續式燈帶和鍍鉻裝飾元素，增添了更型格外觀。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229027" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_1233110-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_1233110-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_1233110.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229028" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_123330-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_123330-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_123330.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229029" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_1500130-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_1500130-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_1500130.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229030" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150640-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150640-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150640.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在動力規格方面，這款 SUV 搭載了先進全電動驅動系統，續航距離最大為 635 公里，輸出功率達 484 千瓦，扭力達 950 牛頓米。4MATIC 全輪驅動系統為標準設備。在快速充電站以直流電充電 15 分鐘後，最高可獲得 220 公里續航距離。而透過封裝的前後電動驅動系統和創新的前軸支撐架，進一步提升了駕駛的穩定性和舒適性。Mercedes-Maybach EQS 680 SUV 最高速度為 210 km/h，0-100 km/h 加速度為 4.4 秒。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229031" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150720-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150720-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150720.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>車廂設計結合了傳統與前衞的元素，採用了 Maybach 的設計理念「What is good must also be beautiful」。車廂中，前排乘客可以使用標準配備的 MBUX Hyberscreen 屏幕，所有三個顯示屏均展示 Mercedes-Maybach 特定的啟動動畫和專屬功能。在電子系統方面，車載配有 MBUX 娛樂資訊系統，提供前後座獨立控制的多功能顯示屏，並支持豐富的定製選項。這包括三種顯示風格（discreet、sporty、MAYBACH）和多種模式（navigation、assistance、service），以滿足不同的使用需求。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229032" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150844-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150844-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150844.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229033" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150916-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150916-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150916.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229041" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151625-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151625-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151625.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229034" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150826-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150826-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150826.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229035" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150741-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150741-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_150741.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229036" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151024-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151024-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151024.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229037" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151104-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151104-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151104.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229038" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151128-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151128-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151128.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>科技系統中，Mercedes-Maybach EQS SUV 配備了各種先進技術，包括自動門的開關控制、MBUX High-End Rear Seat Entertainment 系統以及具有 253 個可控 LED 和 64 種色調的主動式氣氛燈，提供個性化的舒適體驗。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229039" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151210-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151210-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151210.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229040" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151332-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151332-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_151332.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>關於行車安全系統，Mercedes-Maybach EQS SUV 配備了全面的駕駛輔助系統和高效的粒子空氣過濾器（HEPA），以確保駕駛和乘坐的安全性。防撞系統和防噪音效果的提升，保證了車輛在各種行駛條件下的穩定性和安全性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229042" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_152024-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_152024-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_152024.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229043" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_152048-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_152048-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_152048.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229044" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_152107-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_152107-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412_152107.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><div class="page" title="Page 8"><div class="layoutArea"><div class="column"><h2>Mercedes-Maybach EQS 680 SUV 技術規格</h2><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229023" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412101427-591x580.jpg" alt="" width="591" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412101427-591x580.jpg 591w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240412101427.jpg 917w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 591px" /></p></div></div><div class="layoutArea"><div class="column"></div></div></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/13/mercedes-maybach-eqs-680-suv/life-tech/auto/">Mercedes-Maybach EQS 680 SUV 電車到港，雙色系型格車身、超豪內籠搶先睇</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
